  <h1 class="author__heading">This is a heading!</h1>
  <p class="author__body">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Officiis corrupti eveniet perspiciatis ipsum eos quos, ea dignissimos in sapiente tempora corporis obcaecati laudantium. Architecto illum dicta facilis non quos optio.</p>
